text: Mimenicodes cohici is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Lepesme and Stephan von Breuning in 1953. It is known from New Caledonia.BioLib.cz - Mimenicodes cohici. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1953
title: Mimenicodes cohici
